---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Senior Design Project"
  description="Led a multidisciplinary engineering team through a capstone project."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Projects</p>

    <h1>Senior Design Project</h1>

    <p class="intro">
      Led a multidisciplinary team through the planning, design, and execution
      of a capstone engineering project.
    </p>

    <img
      src="/images/projects/senior-design.jpg"
      alt="Senior Design Project"
    />
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Overview</h2>

    <p>
      This capstone project required collaboration between mechanical,
      electrical, and software engineering disciplines.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Process</h2>

    <p>
      Responsibilities included project planning, task delegation, team
      coordination, and ensuring technical objectives were met throughout the
      project lifecycle.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Tools Used</h2>

    <p>Leadership • Project Management • Collaboration</p>
  </section>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 24px;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  section + section {
    margin-top: 4rem;
  }

  .hero {
    max-width: 48rem;
  }

  .intro {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }
</style>